                    </svg>
                    Understand urgency level
                  </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/tools/basement-problem-diagnostic" class="bg-white text-green-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
